  padding: 2rem 1rem 3rem;
}

.back-to-top {
  color: #2563eb;
  text-decoration: none;
}

/* Reflection
   1) Flexbox was a natural fit for the header (brand vs nav),
      the hero actions row, and the album card grid.
      Flex-wrap and flex-basis made the layout responsive.

   2) It was possible but limited to control exact column counts
      with Flexbox. CSS Grid would be better for strict 2/3/4
      column layouts. Flexbox works fine for this lab though.
*/
